[04:56.17]GUIDERIUS	Would I could free't!
[04:58.20]ARVIRAGUS	Or I, whate'er it be,
[05:00.16]	What pain it cost, what danger. God's!
[05:03.32]BELARIUS	Hark, boys.
[05:04.53]	[Whispering]
